span begin="14.194" end="14.611">Thursday,</span> <span begin="14.611" end="15.091">October</span> <span begin="15.091" end="15.424">Twenty-</span><span begin="15.424" end="15.774">second</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">包括波士顿 发表于 10 月 22 日 周四晚 7 时 21 分</span></p><p begin="16.220" end="21.519" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.220" end="16.750">Tonight:</span> <span begin="16.850" end="17.227">Mostly</span> <span begin="17.227" end="17.661">cloudy</span> <span begin="17.661" end="17.904">with</span> <span begin="17.904" end="18.532">isolated</span> <span begin="18.532" end="19.032">showers</span> <span begin="19.032" end="19.372">until</span> <span begin="19.372" end="19.674">midnight,</span> <span begin="19.803" end="20.133">then</span> <span begin="20.133" end="20.592">mostly</span> <span begin="20.592" end="20.832">clear</span> <span begin="20.832" end="21.102">after</span> <span begin="21.102" end="21.519">midnight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">今晚大部多云 局部地区前半夜有阵雨 后半基本无雨</span></p><p begin="21.751" end="23.104" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.751" end="22.065">Lows</span> <span begin="22.065" end="22.104">in</span> <span begin="22.104" end="22.140">the</span> <span begin="22.140" end="22.660">lower</span> <span begin="22.660" end="23.104">40&apos;s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">最低温度近 40℉</span></p><p begin="23.418" end="27.590" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.418" end="23.773">West</span> <span begin="23.773" end="24.065">winds</span> <span begin="24.065" end="24.301">10-</span><span begin="24.301" end="24.797">15</span><span begin="24.797" end="25.568">mph</span> <span begin="25.568" end="25.805">with</span> <span begin="25.805" end="26.140">gusts</span> <span begin="26.140" end="26.330">up</span> <span begin="26.330" end="26.456">to</span> <span begin="26.456" end="26.910">25</span><span begin="26.910" end="27.590">mph</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">西风 10~15mph 最高风速 25mph</span></p><p begin="27.954" end="29.648" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.954" end="28.436">Chance</span> <span begin="28.436" end="28.518">of</span> <span begin="28.518" end="28.821">rain</span> <span begin="28.821" end="29.181">20</span> <span begin="29.181" end="29.648">percent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">降水概率 20%</span></p><p begin="29.995" end="33.686" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.995" end="30.548">Friday:</span> <span begin="30.651" end="31.163">Sunny.</span> <span begin="31.498" end="31.851">Lush</span> <span begin="31.851" end="32.084">color</span> <span begin="32.084" end="32.254">with</span> <span begin="32.254" end="32.606">highs</span> <span begin="32.606" end="32.654">in</span> <span begin="32.654" end="32.748">the</span> <span begin="32.748" end="33.068">lower</span> <span begin="33.068" end="33.518">50</span><span begin="33.518" end="33.686">&apos;s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">周五晴 最高温度近 50℉</span></p><p begin="33.871" end="38.335" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.871" end="34.574">Northwest</span> <span begin="34.574" end="34.874">winds</span> <span begin="34.874" end="35.068">10-</span><span begin="35.068" end="35.646">15</span><span begin="35.646" end="36.266">mph</span> <span begin="36.266" end="36.481">with</span> <span begin="36.481" end="36.814">gusts</span> <span begin="36.814" end="36.929">up</span> <span begin="36.929" end="37.097">to</span> <span begin="37.097" end="37.717">25</span><span begin="37.717" end="38.335">mph</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">西北风 10~15mph 最高风速 25mph</span></p><p begin="38.755" end="40.403" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.755" end="39.126">Friday</span> <span begin="39.126" end="39.491">night,</span> <span begin="39.689" end="40.031">mostly</span> <span begin="40.031" end="40.403">clear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml: